{"word":"G1821 - ἐξαποστέλλω - exapostéllō - ex-ap-os-tel'-lo - Send","slug":"G1821","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐξαποστέλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>exapostéllō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ex-ap-os-tel'-lo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Send"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03BE;&#x03B1;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03BB;&#x03C9; - exapostello&#x0304;</b> - <i>ex-ap-os-tel'-lo</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G649\">G649</a>; to <i>send away forth</i>, that is, (on a mission) to <i>despatch</i>, or (peremptorily) to <i>dismiss:</i> - send (away, forth, out)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3992\">G3992</a>, <a href=\"#/G5570\">G5570</a>, <a href=\"#/G649\">G649</a>, <a href=\"#/G651\">G651</a>, <a href=\"#/G652\">G652</a>"}]}